name: CatMaze with NC
description:
It's up to you to achieve the impossible :)  Warning !!!! The game may seem simple at first, but beware it is very hard at level 4.  Small important point: You hit the wall only once, you return to the beginning of the level :)  

-WASD or ARROWS : control the cat

-WASD and ARROWS : speed up the cat xD
